@{
    ViewBag.Title = "主题演示页面";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>主题系统演示</h1>
                <p class="lead">欢迎使用新的主题系统！点击右上角的设置按钮来体验不同的主题色彩。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">功能特性</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <span class="badge">6</span>
                            多种主题色彩
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <span class="badge">2</span>
                            亮色/暗色模式
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <span class="badge">✓</span>
                            响应式设计
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <span class="badge">✓</span>
                            浮动设置菜单
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-primary">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">使用说明</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>登录系统后，点击右上角的<strong>"⚙️ 主题设置"</strong>按钮</li>
                        <li>选择您喜欢的<strong>主题色彩</strong></li>
                        <li>切换<strong>暗色模式</strong>开关</li>
                        <li>主题设置会自动保存到本地</li>
                        <li>登录页面只显示主题效果，需要登录后才能修改主题</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-success">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">主题预览</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>当前选择的主题色彩会应用到：</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>菜单高亮色</li>
                        <li>按钮背景色</li>
                        <li>链接色彩</li>
                        <li>强调色元素</li>
                        <li>登录页面元素</li>
                    </ul>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">主题色按钮</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="well">
                <h4>主题色彩列表</h4>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div style="background-color: #007bff; height: 40px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>
                        <small>深蓝版</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div style="background-color: #c73e1d; height: 40px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>
                        <small>深红版</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div style="background-color: #0ea5e9; height: 40px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>
                        <small>浅蓝版</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div style="background-color: #10b981; height: 40px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>
                        <small>浅绿版</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div style="background-color: #0891b2; height: 40px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>
                        <small>海蓝版</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div style="background-color: #8b5cf6; height: 40px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>
                        <small>浅紫版</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .page-header {
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        color: var(--text-color-primary);
    }
    
    .panel {
        border-color: var(--border-color);
        background-color: var(--sidebar-bg);
    }
    
    .panel-heading {
        background-color: var(--theme-primary) !important;
        border-color: var(--theme-primary) !important;
        color: white !important;
    }
    
    .panel-body {
        color: var(--text-color-primary);
    }
    
    .well {
        background-color: var(--sidebar-bg);
        border-color: var(--border-color);
        color: var(--text-color-primary);
    }
    
    .list-group-item {
        background-color: var(--sidebar-bg);
        border-color: var(--border-color);
        color: var(--text-color-primary);
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
        background-color: var(--theme-primary) !important;
        border-color: var(--theme-primary) !important;
    }
</style>